{
  "level": "Grade 7 Semester 2",
  "part": "Unit 4",
  "section": "B-1b",
  "tree": {
    "id": "root",
    "text": "Improve Your Eating Habits",
    "emoji": "🏥",
    "state": "emoji",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "intro",
        "text": "Importance of Healthy Eating",
        "emoji": "🌟",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p1",
            "text": "Healthy eating is important for a healthy body and mind.",
            "emoji": "💪",
            "keywords": "important, body, mind",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p2",
            "text": "Both what we eat and how we eat are important!",
            "emoji": "⚖️",
            "highlight": "Both, and",
            "keywords": "what we eat, how we eat",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "fast_food",
        "text": "The Problem with Fast Food",
        "emoji": "🍔",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p3",
            "text": "For example, some people have fast food every week.",
            "emoji": "🍟",
            "highlight": "For example",
            "keywords": "fast food, every week",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "p4",
                "text": "It is easy and delicious!",
                "emoji": "😋",
                "keywords": "easy, delicious",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "p5",
                "text": "But it often has lots of salt, fat, and sugar.",
                "emoji": "🧂",
                "highlight": "But",
                "keywords": "salt, fat, sugar",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "p6",
                "text": "That makes us put on weight.",
                "emoji": "⚖️",
                "highlight": "That",
                "keywords": "put on weight",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "p7",
                "text": "Eating fast food like pizza and hamburgers too often may cause heart problems later.",
                "emoji": "❤️",
                "highlight": "like, too often, later",
                "keywords": "pizza, hamburgers, heart problems",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "p8",
                "text": "If you cook your own meals instead, you can make healthy balanced meals.",
                "emoji": "🍳",
                "highlight": "If, instead",
                "keywords": "cook own meals, balanced",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "breakfast",
        "text": "The Importance of Breakfast",
        "emoji": "🥣",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p9",
            "text": "Eating three meals a day is important.",
            "emoji": "🕒",
            "keywords": "three meals a day",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "p10",
                "text": "But some people don't have breakfast.",
                "emoji": "🚫",
                "highlight": "But",
                "keywords": "don't have breakfast",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "p11",
                    "text": "Maybe they don't feel hungry in the morning, or they are too busy to eat anything.",
                    "emoji": "🏃",
                    "highlight": "Maybe, or, too... to",
                    "keywords": "not hungry, busy",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "p12",
                    "text": "But food gives us energy.",
                    "emoji": "⚡",
                    "highlight": "But",
                    "keywords": "gives us energy",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "p13",
                    "text": "It is easy to feel sleepy and find it hard to focus on our work or studies if we don't eat breakfast.",
                    "emoji": "😴",
                    "highlight": "It is easy to, find it hard to, if",
                    "keywords": "sleepy, hard to focus",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "sweets",
        "text": "Limiting Sweet Things",
        "emoji": "🍭",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p14",
            "text": "Some people also eat too many sweet things.",
            "emoji": "🍦",
            "highlight": "also, too many",
            "keywords": "sweet things",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "p15",
                "text": "Ice cream, sweets, and chocolate are delicious, but they usually have lots of sugar.",
                "emoji": "🍫",
                "highlight": "but",
                "keywords": "ice cream, chocolate, sugar",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "p16",
                "text": "This can cause tooth problems.",
                "emoji": "🦷",
                "highlight": "This",
                "keywords": "tooth problems",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "p17",
                "text": "When you want a snack, why don't you have some fruit instead?",
                "emoji": "🍎",
                "highlight": "When, why don't you, instead",
                "keywords": "snack, fruit",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "p18",
                "text": "After all, an apple a day keeps the doctor away.",
                "emoji": "🩺",
                "highlight": "After all",
                "keywords": "apple a day",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "conclusion",
        "text": "Conclusion",
        "emoji": "📝",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p19",
            "text": "Remember: You are what you eat.",
            "emoji": "🧠",
            "keywords": "You are what you eat",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p20",
            "text": "Healthy eating means eating healthy food and having good eating habits.",
            "emoji": "🥗",
            "highlight": "and",
            "keywords": "healthy food, habits",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
